quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,94,"Aan Annabiijo, yo A wii …ďe: onon yahuud en so tawii o…óon njogii aljanna to laakara tawa alaa go…ó…óo naatoowo toon tanaa mon; nji…óee maayde …óa…ď…ďon nde; mbela ke…ďon …óum ko yaawi, poofto-…óon e tampere nguurndam aduna, so tawii o…óon ngoon…óini ndee noddoore mon."
  2,95,"∆Āe nji…óataa maayde pooma; sabu jeddi Alla …ói …ďe ngardini e nguurndam ma…ď…ďe, e fennude Nulaa…ďe Makko, e waylude defte ma…ď…ďe, Alla Mo humpitii too√Īoo…ďe e ma…ď…ďe, maa O yo…ďu gooto kala e golle mum."
  2,96,"Maa a taw -Aan Annabiijo -Yahuud en ngoni …ďur…ďe reer…óude e nguurndam,hay so …óam wonii koy…óam,…ďuri reer…óude kadi …ďeen renndin…ďe e Alla …ďe goon…óinaani ummital e hiiseede,hay so …ďe ngonii yim…ďe deftere,gooto e ma…ď…ďe na yi…óa wuurde duu…ďi ujunere, o wo…ó…óataa lette Alla kala no nguurndam makko juutiri, Alla tigi Mo ∆īellitii e golleeji ma…ď…ďe,alaa ko suu…óantoo Mo heen,maa O yo…ď …ďe …óe."
  2,97,"Wii - Aan Annabiijo - …ďeen Yuhuud en wii…ďe: "wonde Jibriil ko ga√Īo amen e malaykaa…ďe …ďe": Oon ga√Ī…óo Jibriin yo anndu ko e makko Kur'aan on jippori maa e yamiroore Alla, nde goon…óini defte Alla gadii…óe …óe; wano Tawreeta e Injiila, o woni tinndinoowo mo∆ī∆īere, beltiniroowo goon…óin…ďe ko Alla resani …ďe e mo∆ī∆īereeji, ga√Ī…óo jooma …óii sifaaji e golle oon jeyaa ko e majju…ďe."
  2,98,"∆Āeen a√Ī…ďe Alla e nulaa…ďe Mum, …ďe nga√Īi malaykaa…ďe …ói…óo …ďaditii…ďe Alla: Jibriil e Mika'iil; ko Alla woni ga√Īo heefer…ďe, te kala mbo Alla woni ga√Īo mum o he…ďii perte mawnde."
  2,99,"Goonga tigi, Min njippinii e Maa - Aan Annabiijo - maandeeji tinndinooji goon…óinal Maa…óa e annabaagal e wahyu ko ngaddu-…óaa, no …óum laa…ďiri alaa jeddoowo …óum sonaa yaltu…ďe diine Alla o."
  2,100,"Na jeyaa e malkiseede Yahuud en, kala nde …ďe …ďami aadi - wano goon…óinde ko Tawreeta tinndini e annabaagal Muhammadu (jkm) - wooda e ma…ď…ďe firtu…ďe oon aadi, nganndee ko …ďuri heewde e …ďee Yahuudee…ďe goon…óintaa ko Alla jippini; sabu goon…óingol na …óa…ď…ďi timminde aadi."
  2,101,"Nde Muhammadu (jkm) nelaa…óo iwde e Alla ari e ma…ď…ďe, tawii sifa makko arii nder Tawreeta, sete e ma…ď…ďe …óuurnii ndeen tinndinoore, …ďe calii wondeede …óum, …ďe mba'i no majju…óo mbo waawataa naftorde goonga e peewal gonngal heen, o faaletaake (wondetaake) …óum."